{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UWhfvpNf2ZMGCh4yDSSMAd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The 3-node CockroachDB cluster is fully deployed and healthy. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n**Resources deployed:**\n- **Headless Service** `crdb-cluster` — `clusterIP: None`, selects on the required label pair, exposes ports 26257 (grpc) and 8080 (http). `publishNotReadyAddresses: true` so DNS resolves during startup.\n- **Public Service** `crdb-cluster-public` — ClusterIP service on the same ports for client access.\n- **StatefulSet** `crdb-cluster` — 3 replicas, `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` (required so all 3 nodes start simultaneously before the cluster is initialized), image `cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0`, insecure mode, each pod advertises itself via its FQDN and joins all 3 peer DNS names.\n- **PodDisruptionBudget** `crdb-cluster-pdb` — `minAvailable: 2`, ensuring quorum is preserved during voluntary disruptions.\n- **3 PVCs** — each `10Gi` RWO, all Bound.\n\nAll 3 nodes report `is_available=true` and `is_live=true`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":496,"cache_read_input_tokens":37197,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":496},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"feda8da2-702b-4864-9a5d-26995f79f87e","uuid":"fed688f9-bac2-4722-aba4-23647739606a","request_id":"req_011Ccc94qCXhnTS3nP8844j5"}
